d release them in the map!\nThe left and right sticks allow you to move the user's position slightly.\n\n[Type of Units]\n-Base\nThis is the Base.\nBuild your Base stronger!!\n\n-Fighter\nA common flying unit.\nGround & Air Attack.\n\n-Factory\nA factory unit.\nIt generates cash.\n\n-Bomber\nA flying unit skilled for\nbombing and ground attack.\n\n-Tank\nAn anti-ground unit.\nAttacks with rapid fire.\n\n-Anti-aircraft Artillery\nA placement unit using missles.\nEffective to flying units.\n\n-Sheild\nA placement unit for defense.\nIt has high durability.\n", "short_description": "Let's play a VR video game with your girl friend!\nThis time it's a strategy game.\nPick up the units and release them in the map.\nThe units will start fighting automatically."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "PdpArt_3000x900_JP.png", "id": "266102791924715", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974650_266102795258048_1135847423250422851_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=G7aHDjIyk8YQ7kNvgGoHPS3&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AIahJLHaXCKwvkyQCGlvFhK&oh=00_AYAY__MxFwT5kXv1OFP2pLzUzbZw_34rL6ylPpyRi1EpTA&oe=66E963B4"}, {"file_name": "Art_1008x1440.png", "id": "4244000545622202", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974522_4244000548955535_6121386002098751284_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=7_HoHWUwW6wQ7kNvgEAHXp6&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AIahJLHaXCKwvkyQCGlvFhK&oh=00_AYCc_4S9dp9bz3UMbIbHhZMwHheQpB2Q5iPNxg-vqlynPg&oe=66E98445"}, {"file_name": "Art_2560x1440.png", "id": "3609745079249612", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974800_3609745082582945_8822499596742085698_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=_rJKjO4NZGoQ7kNvgEXMlCH&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AIahJLHaXCKwvkyQCGlvFhK&oh=00_AYBS7L2gs9Kj9zJORsvtxTjL1OAdaReFUWNxKZBHg70rPg&oe=66E97C0C"}, {"file_na